        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for criticisms of <hi rend="italic">Colour-sense</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Clarifies his views that actions desirable for species result in development of nervous organs capable of pleasurable stimulation.</p>
            <p>Believes that all "tastes" occurring in nature are explicable with reference to ancestral habits and that none is purely arbitrary.</p>
        </abstract>
